Fetch physiological attribute data

attribute.Rd

Fetch physiological attribute data

attribute(keyword = "all")

Arguments

keyword

a character vector of attribute names desired. For the available attributes, run bugphyzz::attribute_list()

Value

a large list of tidy data.frames

Examples

x <- attribute()
head(x[[1]])
